{
  "texts": [
    "Tuesday, 2nd March of 2022.",
    "I join the Water Day Protest in Santiago, Chile's capital.",
    "A popular slogan at the rally is 'no es sequía, es saqueo' [this is not a drought, this is a robbery].",
    "Protestors range from local communities to Indigenous people and workers' unions.",
    "The march finishes in the offices of the Constituent Assembly, where topics such as the 'rights of nature' are debated by democratically elected representatives."
  ]
}